    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. The high-revving S54 power plant features a 3.2L displacement with a forged crankshaft and graphite-coated pistons, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. This example retains its factory-correct 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is impeccably preserved, showing zero subframe fatigue, and the Double VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure precise cam phasing. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this unit exhibits zero mechanical lash and remains in a showroom-ready state, representing the pinnacle of the analog driving experience.",
