      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing a flawless factory finish and a mechanically superlative powertrain. The S54 inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with the critical dual-VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe structurally reinforced for long-term chassis rigidity. This example features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque through a pristine M-Variable differential. Every bushing, link, and damper remains within tight tolerances, ensuring the communicative steering and neutral handling balance these chassis are renowned for. The interior exhibits zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather, and the undercarriage is devoid of oxidation or fluid seepage. A comprehensive service dossier accompanies this concours-ready specimen.",
